data.description: Beautiful Views of the lake, golf course and surrounding areas out the back of this spacious 3 bedroom , 2 bath triplewide manufactured home with a 2 car attached garage and a 2048 sq ft shop with 4 garage doors. Spacious kitchen with island, nook, pantry area, large living room with propane fireplace, Primary room has an extra room for office/nursery/gym, jetted tub and double sinks. Back covered patio, a garden shed & room for all your toys. Call today for a showing!
